{
  "description": "The image depicts Alcatraz Island in San Francisco Bay, dominated by the infamous former prison. The prison building, a multi-story white structure with dark windows, is perched atop a rocky island covered in patches of green vegetation. Behind Alcatraz, the San Francisco skyline is visible, a dense collection of buildings and hills. The hills are primarily green and brown, with buildings interspersed among them. The water of the bay is a deep blue, with slight ripples and waves. The sky is clear and a vibrant blue. The overall scene evokes a sense of history, isolation, and the dramatic beauty of the San Francisco Bay Area.",
